     C           BATOKU    ANDEQ#KTOKU
TCHK1C*          BANONY    ANDEQ#KNONY
TCHK1C           BANONY    LOKUPNON                      91
TCHK1C  N91                ITER
      *
     C*****      @NUKE     IFNE *BLANK
